<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-86-1465 </DOCNO><TEXT>In this paper, by using the collective coordinate of Bohr and phenomenologicaldeformed optical potentials, the scattering amplitudes of two composite-particlesystems can be obtained. And the collective excitation for two composite-particalsystems in the scattering process is discussed.</TEXT></DOC>